4.82/5  rDev +8.6%look: 4.5 | smell: 5 | taste: 5 | feel: 4.5 |  overall: 4.5750mL corked & capped bottle poured into a stemmed glass. 2006 vintage, bottledon Sept. 1st, 2008. 
