M-Acidic and sour, with low to medium carbonation and medium weight body. Quite good.
D- This is a great lambic. I wish I would have gotten into Cantillon earlier! This is a great sour that offers lots of authentic raspberry flavors and is quite tart. 884 charactersPittBeerGirl, Apr 29, 2010
